description: Digital collage about on the innocence of young people and children, when lacking a hostile environment. At the same time, serves as an analogy of the human being as a transforming agent of changes in your cosmos, individual or collective, in this case, represented by the planets. The colors of the backgrounds, mixed with the landscape of the interstellar space, also put as a counterpoint the volatility of current times, whether caused by digital media and for our more consumerist relationships,
